{"id": "1224352677010477136", "channel_id": "1224352677010477136", "type": 0, "author_id": "1191620861699031083", "author_name": "dulce_lxy", "author_bot": false, "content": "好早之前就有注意到，艾瑞卡的0费牌经常打着打着等级就变成一级的了。进图的时候是满级的技能然后过一会就变成一级的了，印出来的打击和防御也是一级的。这个bug太坑了，真得快快修复🥹", "timestamp": "2024-04-01T13:40:25.572000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 8}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1224352677010477136", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」艾瑞卡恶性bug反馈", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
