{"id": "1224289875881230346", "channel_id": "1224289875881230346", "type": 0, "author_id": "733514425847513171", "author_name": "xuan4185", "author_bot": false, "content": "已知造物須臾的火跟深潛寧菲亞的事件可以將選到的指令卡進行複製（可能還有其他會複製指令卡並加入牌庫的東東，但是我不記得了），其中須臾的火是會把選中的卡牌（原始？）複製到牌庫中且不會一併複製刻印，而寧菲亞事件則是完完整整包括刻印全都給你複製。\n原本我以為須臾的火是把選的卡乾乾淨淨的塞到牌庫，但今天發現它連同檔案夾賦予女王之劍固有保留抽一張牌都一起複製了，想知道這些不同的複製區別到底是什麼", "timestamp": "2024-04-01T09:30:52.616000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1224289876266975292", "filename": "Screenshot_20240401_123203.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 189565, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1224289875881230346/1224289876266975292/Screenshot_20240401_123203.jpg?ex=6a00504c&is=69fefecc&hm=f232f4f1f216c79eed288a48750c84ee7613114dc077e7db334cec909ec79c38&"}, {"id": "1224289876707643430", "filename": "Screenshot_20240401_124122.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 182959, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1224289875881230346/1224289876707643430/Screenshot_20240401_124122.jpg?ex=6a00504c&is=69fefecc&hm=e0f65d5bedab63395eab824d860414769d856967b835b755d7b300c563015d27&"}, {"id": "1224289877227470859", "filename": "V4_-_-_20240317.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 258289, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1224289875881230346/1224289877227470859/V4_-_-_20240317.jpg?ex=6a00504c&is=69fefecc&hm=63c4d3e2d0877fa25c263f3572549746215f20b609149709774632047e6e7ec3&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1224289875881230346", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "對於複製卡牌的事件與造物的問題", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
